      "rationale": "Three meshes generated with refinement ratio 1.5: coarse (2.1M cells), medium (4.7M cells), fine (10.6M cells). GCI for relative hemolysis index computed as 2.8% between medium and fine grids. Medium mesh adopted for production runs, providing adequate accuracy at acceptable computational cost."
    },
