      "rationale": "Maximum deviation between CFD-predicted and measured RH index was 13.4% at the highest flow-speed combination. Bland-Altman analysis yielded limits of agreement of ±18.7% with mean bias of +1.2%, indicating no clinically significant systematic offset. All 5 operating points within acceptance criteria."
